{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_153b42b9dee7a67824a68d28", "problem_id": "prob_9ac231b846f1124a2961b00b", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "10", "normalized_question_text": "如图所示是一做匀变速直线运动的质点的位置-时间图象（x-t图象），P（t1，x1）为图象上一点。PQ为过P点的切线，与x轴交于点Q（0，x2）。已知t=0时质点的速度大小为v0，则下列说法正确的是", "normalized_answer_text": "质点的加速度大小为$\\frac{x_{1}-x_{2}}{t_{1}^{2}}-\\frac{v_{0}}{t_{1}}$", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "good", "solvability_score": 1.0, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "pass", "decision_reason_codes": ["rewrite_usable", "semantically_complete", "solvable_and_aligned"], "created_at": "2026-04-04T17:03:36Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_18f5acb8aeeb1f729cefcfb1", "problem_id": "prob_8b14c5dce2f8482bfbc98481", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "57", "normalized_question_text": "A、B两物体同时同地从静止出发做直线运动，物体的加速度与时间关系如题图所示，其中$t_{2}=2t_{1}$。关于两个物体的运动，下列判断正确的是：", "normalized_answer_text": "$t_{2}$时刻，两物体速度相同", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "good", "solvability_score": 1.0, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "pass", "decision_reason_codes": ["answer_available", "jointly_understandable", "rewrite_usable"], "created_at": "2026-04-04T18:05:33Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_31568e96add921449424c0d9", "problem_id": "prob_439ce68098464f5d04ecd2ef", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "71", "normalized_question_text": "如图所示，A、B两物体相距x=7m，物体A以$v_A=4\\mathrm{~m/s}$的速度向右匀速运动，而物体B此时的速度$v_B=10\\mathrm{~m/s}$，只在摩擦力作用下向右做匀减速运动，加速度大小为$a=2\\mathrm{~m/s^2}$，那么物体A追上物体B所用的时间为", "normalized_answer_text": "8s", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "good", "solvability_score": 1.0, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "pass", "decision_reason_codes": ["answer_available", "rewrite_usable", "solvable_and_aligned", "text_sufficient"], "created_at": "2026-04-04T18:23:03Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_8bf3c5425fc4a17be8f99473", "problem_id": "prob_09d53951d7f0473547fb3e48", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "83", "normalized_question_text": "一圆形金属环与两固定的平行长直导线在同一竖直面内，环的圆心与两导线距离相等，环的直径小于两导线间距。两导线中通有大小相等、方向向下的恒定电流。若（ ）", "normalized_answer_text": "金属环向右侧直导线靠近，则环上的感应电流方向为逆时针方向", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": false, "text_dominant": true, "cleaning_path": "text_lightweight", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 2, "alignment_status": "good", "solvability_score": 1.0, "solvability_path_mode": "text_only", "clean_decision": "pass", "decision_reason_codes": ["answer_available", "split_open_usable", "text_sufficient"], "created_at": "2026-04-04T18:39:04Z"}
